//////
Intro() =>
  about = `
    - This list uses some descriptions made by Chat GPT and Gemini, and others descriptions are made based on web research and danbooru tags.
    - This means that most of the outfits here are made to be used in t2i generators, in anime style, I dont know how well it works in realistic.
    - It also uses dynamic negatives, you dont have to worry if you dont want it, but if you want them, you need to look up in the code on the https://perchance.org/ai-art-generator-advanced, how the LocalTempFashion works.
    - Some descriptions are written in a weird way because it is the only way they work in perchance, also, skirts in anime style are harder, the ai likes red pleated skirt so much.
  `
AdvRS = {import:adv-random-styles}
// Please give credits in the painel of your generator, you can copy past the line below to import:
// Fashion = {import:female-outfit-list-flux} // Made by BlackYT👄🍆 - AI ART GENERATOR ADVANCED


////////////////
Fabric
  //Lurex (lack data)
  🎲 Random Fabric/Texture (32)
    [AdvRS('Fabric', banFabric = ['🎲 Random Fabric/Texture (32)'], Fabric), FabricRandomItem]


  /// Smooth
  Chiffon //A lightweight, sheer fabric known for its smooth, flowing texture. It's often used for flowing skirts, blouses, and overlays.
    made of chiffon fabric, with gauze quality, gossamer texture, rich in sheer and shimmery //, (chiffon texture:1.4)
  Crepe // OK, updated flux
    made from crêpe, a fabric with crinkled or pebbled texture, with grainy appearance, giving the clothes a textured matte finishh //
  Mesh
    made of mesh, a lightweight material with a nettexture that features a gridpattern of small holes
  Microfiber //Offers a very smooth and soft texture.
    made of microfiber, fabric soft and lightweight, with an ultra-fine texture. provides a sleek finish and modern aesthetic
  Polyester //Can be engineered to mimic the smoothness of natural fibers like silk.
    made of smooth polyester, resilient texture providing a sleek fabric, ensures a polished appearance
  Rayon //Provides a silky smoothness at a slightly lower cost than silk.
    made of rayon, fabric that features smooth texture{, enhancing any clothes with a subtle sheen^0.6|^1.5}
  Satin //Known for its lustrous, smooth surface.
    made of satin, fabric with smooth surface, giving the lustrous satin texture
  Silk //Offers a luxurious, silky feel.
    made of silk, lustrous, offers a luxurious, silky feel, silky texture
  Spandex //A synthetic fabric with excellent elasticity. While it can have a slightly textured appearance when used alone, it's often blended with other fabrics to create a smooth, stretchy material.
    made of spandex, fabric with smooth, sleek appearance, its glossy surface gives the clothes a polished look
  Suede //A soft, leather-like material with a smooth finish.
    made of suede fabric, that has a plush texture, giving the clothes a subtle depth
  Taffeta
    made from taffeta fabric, a crisp, smooth and tightly woven fabric, plain taffeta texture
  Tulle
    made with tulle fabric, lightweight, very fine, stiff netting //, tulle texture
  Velvet //While it has a plush appearance, its surface is typically smooth.
    made of velvet, a fabric with plush texture, and a soft sheen that enhances its velvet texture

  /// Rough
  Bouclé //A yarn with loops or curls, creating a textured fabric.
    made of boucle fabric, boucle texture. Has a looped, textured fabric that feels  soft, its distinctive yarn loops create a plush texture //

  Burlap //A coarse, heavy fabric with a rough, rustic appearance.
    made of burlap, that has a coarse, rough texture, with visible fibers woven in a loose, open pattern{, making the fabric visually raw, giving it a rustic aesthetic|}
  Chinchilla //This luxurious fur has a dense, rough texture.
    made of chinchilla fur fabric, dense chinchilla fur texture, has an incredibly plush feel and velvety surface, its fine fibers create a smooth, cushiony feel //
  Chunky knit //Creates a bulky, textured look.
    made of chunky knit, chunky knit texture, creates a cozy, plush look, adding dimension to the outfit
  Corduroy //A fabric with raised, parallel ridges, creating a textured appearance.
    made of corduroy fabric, corduroy texture, fabric with ribbed texture, consisting of parallel ridges
  Denim //Offers a rugged, textured look.
    made of denim, a twill-woven fabric. The material has a rugged, slightly coarse surface.
  Faux fur //Provides a soft but textured feel.
    made of faux fur fabric, faux fur texture, offering a dense, plush texture. Its fibers have a luxurious feel that creates depth //
  Lace //Can have a delicate yet textured appearance, depending on the type of lace.
    made of lace, fabric with lace texture. Its fine, sheer appearance often adds a feminine touch while offering a soft, elegant finish
  Latex //A synthetic material known for its elasticity and shine. While it can be smooth, it often has a slightly textured or glossy appearance, especially when used in thicker or patterned forms.
    made of latex, a smooth, high-gloss fabric, known for its tight, skin-like fit and reflective texture, its glossy finish makes a sleek outfit
  Leather //A natural material with a distinct, textured surface. While it can be smoothed and polished, it typically retains a certain roughness. In dresses, leather is often used for accents, details, or full-length skirts.
    made of leather, sleek, smoothed and polished, retains a certain roughness from leather texture //
  Linen //Known for its wrinkled, natural texture.
    made of linen fabric, linen texture, that has slightly textured surface, its lightweight, slightly coarse fibers create a crisp appearance that softens
  Tweed //A coarse, woolen fabric with a distinctive pattern and texture.
    made of tweed fabric, tweed texture, a textured fabric, featuring a rough, nubby surface with visible fibers

  /// Special
  Cloth of gold
    made from gold cloth, cloth of gold, fabric woven with a gold-wrapped, spun gold strip
  Foil Shimmer
    all made of foil shimmer, with a reflective, holographic texture
    //made of foil shimmer, with beautiful visual effect that have holographic texture, rainbow iridescence, reflective surface, prismatic shine, metallic light scattering, micro square pattern
  Foil Shimmer+
    all made of foil shimmer, with a reflective, holographic texture, and micro-square pattern that scatters a metallic light with a prismatic shine
  Glitter Satin
    made from glitter satin, features glittery elements incorporated into the satin weave, adding a subtle shimmer to the fabric
  Grid Net
    all made of a grid net material
  Lamé
    made from lamé fabric, fabric made with metallic fiber, metallic sheen, is a luxurious fabric //, lamé texture
  Mesh Lace
    made from mesh lace embellished with glittery details, such as {metallic threads|glitter-coated surfaces}
  Metallic
    made from metallic fabric, incorporates metallic threads, metallic fibers, creating a lustrous and reflective outfit surface{, with a subtle metallic sheen|, with bold}, high-shine finishes, metallic texture
  Plastic
    made of a plastic-like material, transparent fabric that completely revels the character skin, exposing the body underneath
  Sequin
    made with shiny sequin, decorated with sequin, sequin texture
  Sheer fabric
    made from sheer fabric, the sheer texture accentuates the wearer's allure.
  Slimy
    made of a slimy-like material, the fabric has a sticky texture, with a transparency that revels the body underneath
